tool_description:
**CodeROG's Random User API**

Short Description:
Generate random user profiles with customizable attributes for testing, development, and placeholder data. Access diverse user data, including names, locations, contact info, and more. Ideal for populating apps and websites with realistic user information.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://random-user-api.p.rapidapi.com/api"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "random-user-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
